{"word":"ἐπιτρέφω","slug":"ἐπιτρέφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιτρέφω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-θρέψω</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-τέτροφα</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐπετράφην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to rear upon</i>:—generally, <i>to support, maintain</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to grow up after</i>, as posterity, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>succrescere</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <i>to grow up as a successor</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}